## Patent grant

Both AGPLv3 (§ 11) and PolyForm Noncommercial 1.0.0 ("Patent License")
include patent grants from the licensor.  Both also include patent
defense / retaliation clauses that terminate your patent license if
you sue the licensor (or contributors) for patent infringement related
to Mazemaker.

